title: Yacht Rock Soundtrack, Show, and Extras
description:
This torrent includes the Yacht Rock series (including the episode 2 long cut), all the songs used in the show, the SCTV parody featured in the show, the Channel101 Yacht Rock Snickers "commercial", a JD Ryznar update, the Channel 101 musical, and a bunch of still images.

Only things missing are the Benedictine Chant that opened up episode four and the fight Q&A videos that JZ Ryznar did, which he's made private on Youtube.
